<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Lu — Portfolio de Desarrollo</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:       #0A0A0B;
  --bg2:      #111113;
  --bg3:      #18181C;
  --border:   rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --border2:  rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  --text:     #E8E6E0;
  --text2:    #8A8880;
  --text3:    #4A4845;
  --accent:   #C8FF00;
  --accent2:  #5B6EFF;
  --red:      #FF4D4D;
  --amber:    #F5A623;
  --green:    #2DCA72;
  --mono:     'DM Mono', monospace;
  --sans:     'Syne', sans-serif;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── Noise overlay ────────────────────────────────── */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9999;
  opacity: 0.4;
}

/* ── Nav ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
nav {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 16px 48px;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  background: rgba(10,10,11,0.85);
}

.nav-logo {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}

.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 32px;
  list-style: none;
}

.nav-links a {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text2);
  text-decoration: none;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

/* ── Sections ─────────────────────────────────────── */
section { padding: 120px 48px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }

/* ── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding-top: 120px;
  position: relative;
  max-width: none;
}

.hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px; }

.hero-tag {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s forwards;
}

.hero-name {
  font-size: clamp(56px, 10vw, 128px);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 0.92;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.2s forwards;
}

.hero-name span { color: var(--accent); }

.hero-desc {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--text2);
  max-width: 560px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 56px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.35s forwards;
}

.hero-stats {
  display: flex;
  gap: 48px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.5s forwards;
}

.hero-stat-n {
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  color: var(--text);
}

.hero-stat-l {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text3);
  font-family: var(--mono);
  margin-top: 2px;
}

.hero-grid {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(200,255,0,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200,255,0,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 80px 80px;
  pointer-events: none;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 80% at 70% 50%, black, transparent);
}

/* ── Section headers ──────────────────────────────── */
.section-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  line-height: 1.05;
  margin-bottom: 64px;
}

/* ── Projects ─────────────────────────────────────── */
.projects { padding-top: 40px; }

.project-card {
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  background: var(--bg2);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
}

.project-card:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }

.project-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 24px;
  padding: 32px 36px;
  cursor: pointer;
  user-select: none;
}

.project-num {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text3);
  margin-top: 4px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 28px;
}

.project-info { flex: 1; }

.project-name {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.project-sub {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text2);
  font-family: var(--mono);
}

.project-meta {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.tag {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border2);
  color: var(--text2);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

.tag-accent { border-color: rgba(200,255,0,0.3); color: var(--accent); }
.tag-blue   { border-color: rgba(91,110,255,0.3); color: var(--accent2); }
.tag-amber  { border-color: rgba(245,166,35,0.3); color: var(--amber); }
.tag-green  { border-color: rgba(45,202,114,0.3); color: var(--green); }

.chevron {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--text3);
  transition: transform 0.3s;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 2px;
}

.project-card.open .chevron { transform: rotate(90deg); }

.project-body {
  display: none;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  padding: 36px;
}

.project-card.open .project-body { display: block; }

/* ── Two-col layout ───────────────────────────────── */
.two-col {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 32px;
}

.three-col {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
}

/* ── Stat boxes ───────────────────────────────────── */
.stat-box {
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 20px 22px;
}

.stat-box-n {
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.stat-box-l {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text2);
  font-family: var(--mono);
}

/* ── Progress bars ────────────────────────────────── */
.prog-section { margin-top: 28px; }

.prog-title {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  color: var(--text3);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.prog-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.prog-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text2);
  width: 160px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.prog-track {
  flex: 1;
  height: 3px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 10px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.prog-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 10px;
  transition: width 1s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
}

.prog-pct {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text3);
  width: 36px;
  text-align: right;
}

/* ── Layer blocks ─────────────────────────────────── */
.layer-block {
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 20px 22px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.layer-block-title {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.layer-block-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ── Code snippets ────────────────────────────────── */
.code-block {
  background: #0D0D10;
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 18px 20px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-top: 12px;
  overflow-x: auto;
}

.code-block .kw { color: var(--accent2); }
.code-block .str { color: var(--accent); }
.code-block .cm { color: var(--text3); font-style: italic; }
.code-block .fn { color: #FF9F7F; }
.code-block .num { color: var(--amber); }

/* ── Version evolution ────────────────────────────── */
.version-track {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0;
  margin: 24px 0;
  position: relative;
}

.version-track::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 20px;
  left: 20px;
  right: 20px;
  height: 0.5px;
  background: var(--border2);
}

.version-step {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  position: relative;
}

.version-dot {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border2);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  z-index: 1;
}

.version-step.done .version-dot {
  background: rgba(200,255,0,0.1);
  border-color: rgba(200,255,0,0.4);
  color: var(--accent);
}

.version-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text3);
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

/* ── Files list ───────────────────────────────────── */
.files-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.file-pill {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 8px 12px;
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text2);
}

.file-dot {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.file-lines {
  margin-left: auto;
  color: var(--text3);
  font-size: 10px;
}

.badge-new {
  font-size: 9px;
  padding: 2px 6px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: rgba(200,255,0,0.12);
  color: var(--accent);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(200,255,0,0.25);
  margin-left: auto;
}

/* ── Market section ───────────────────────────────── */
.market-cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 48px;
}

.market-card {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 28px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
}

.market-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--border2);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.market-icon {
  font-size: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.market-title {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}

.market-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.market-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 14px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

/* ── Issues resolved ──────────────────────────────── */
.issue-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; }

.issue-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 12px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.ib { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
.ib-r { background: rgba(255,77,77,0.12); color: var(--red); border: 0.5px solid rgba(255,77,77,0.2); }
.ib-a { background: rgba(245,166,35,0.12); color: var(--amber); border: 0.5px solid rgba(245,166,35,0.2); }
.ib-g { background: rgba(45,202,114,0.12); color: var(--green); border: 0.5px solid rgba(45,202,114,0.2); }

/* ── Closing ──────────────────────────────────────── */
.closing {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 120px 48px;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.closing-quote {
  font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 32px);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  line-height: 1.3;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  color: var(--text);
}

.closing-quote em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--accent);
}

/* ── Footer ───────────────────────────────────────── */
footer {
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  padding: 32px 48px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.footer-l { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3); }
.footer-r { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3); }

/* ── Animations ───────────────────────────────────── */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(24px);
  transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
}
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

/* ── Divider ──────────────────────────────────────── */
.divider {
  height: 0.5px;
  background: var(--border);
  margin: 0 48px;
}

/* ── Sub-section title ────────────────────────────── */
.sub-title {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  margin-top: 24px;
  color: var(--text);
}

.sub-title:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

/* ── Inline mono ──────────────────────────────────── */
code {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  padding: 2px 6px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  color: var(--accent);
}

p { margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--text2); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }
p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">LU.DEV</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#proyectos">Proyectos</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ecosistema">Ecosistema</a></li>
    <li><a href="#mercado">Mercado</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contacto">Contacto</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-tag">Portfolio de desarrollo · 2026</div>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Lu<br><span>Builder.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      20 años. Desarrollo independiente. Cuatro proyectos de software
      que evolucionaron hasta formar un ecosistema propio con
      orquestación central, seguridad criptográfica y control robótico.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-stat-n">8.000+</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-l">líneas en producción</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-stat-n">4</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-l">proyectos integrados</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-stat-n">C++ · Py · Dart</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-l">stack completo</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ── PROYECTOS ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="proyectos">
  <div class="section-eyebrow reveal">Trabajo</div>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal">Cuatro sistemas.<br>Un ecosistema.</h2>

  <!-- P1: CITRA -->
  <div class="project-card reveal" id="p1">
    <div class="project-header" onclick="toggle('p1')">
      <div class="project-num">01</div>
      <div class="project-info">
        <div class="project-name">CITRA Robotics</div>
        <div class="project-sub">Sistema robótico fullstack · seguridad criptográfica · 6.129 líneas</div>
      </div>
      <div class="project-meta">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">C++17</span>
        <span class="tag tag-blue">Python</span>
        <span class="tag">ZMQ</span>
        <span class="tag">OpenSSL</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chevron">›</div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-body">

      <div class="three-col" style="margin-bottom:32px">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-box-n" style="color:var(--accent2)">738</div>
          <div class="stat-box-l">líneas C++ backend</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-box-n" style="color:var(--amber)">5.145</div>
          <div class="stat-box-l">líneas frontend web</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-box-n" style="color:var(--green)">6</div>
          <div class="stat-box-l">páginas de producto</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <div class="sub-title">Arquitectura — 5 capas</div>

          <div class="layer-block">
            <div class="layer-block-title">
              <span style="color:var(--accent2)">●</span> Núcleo C++ concurrente
            </div>
            <div class="layer-block-desc">
              Motor de 100ms con <code>std::thread</code>, <code>std::mutex</code>, <code>condition_variable</code> y <code>atomic&lt;bool&gt;</code>. Cola de comandos asíncrona. <code>compare_exchange_strong</code> para start/stop sin race conditions. Telemetría por callback serializada a JSON.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="layer-block">
            <div class="layer-block-title">
              <span style="color:var(--red)">●</span> Seguridad criptográfica
            </div>
            <div class="layer-block-desc">
              <code>HMAC()</code> con <code>EVP_sha256()</code>. <code>CRYPTO_memcmp()</code> para comparación timing-safe — evita timing attacks reales. <code>OPENSSL_cleanse()</code> en destructor de <code>SecureString</code> para zeroize en memoria. Integrity chain tipo blockchain liviana con SHA-256 encadenado.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="layer-block">
            <div class="layer-block-title">
              <span style="color:var(--amber)">●</span> Honeypot + Bridge
            </div>
            <div class="layer-block-desc">
              Detección de intrusiones en archivos. Rate limiting 60 eventos/min por fuente. Ventana anti-replay ±5 minutos. Bridge Python/ZMQ: comandos por PUSH/PULL, estado por HTTP GET. <code>SNDHWM=10</code> y <code>LINGER=0</code> para shutdown limpio.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="sub-title">Frontend — 2 sistemas de diseño</div>
          <div class="files-grid" style="margin-top:0">
            <div class="file-pill"><div class="file-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>roboapp-landing<div class="file-lines">1.079</div></div>
            <div class="file-pill"><div class="file-dot" style="background:var(--accent2)"></div>neurogente-mobile<div class="file-lines">1.488</div></div>
            <div class="file-pill"><div class="file-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>roboapp-ecosystem<div class="file-lines">1.137</div></div>
            <div class="file-pill"><div class="file-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>roboapp-b2b<div class="file-lines">506</div></div>
            <div class="file-pill"><div class="file-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>roboapp-account<div class="file-lines">485</div></div>
            <div class="file-pill"><div class="file-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>roboapp-emails<div class="file-lines">444</div></div>
          </div>

          <div class="sub-title" style="margin-top:24px">Evolución v1 → v4</div>
